      "frFR": "Burning Metamagic Rod",
      "frFR": "This rod grants its wielder the ability to make up to three spells they cast per day burning, as though using the Burning Spell feat.\nRegular rods can be used with spells of 6th level or lower.\nBurning Spell: When a creature takes acid or fire damage from the affected spell, that creature takes damage equal to 2x the spell’s actual level at the start of its next turn. The damage is acid or fire, as determined by the spell’s descriptor.",
